Title: Provides for the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; repealer
Summary: Provides for the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; defines the practice thereof.
LawCode: Rpld §§8004 & 8005, amd Ed L, generally; amd §§413 & 488, Soc Serv L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law and the social services law, in relation to the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; and repealing certain provisions of the education law relating thereto
